# Multimedia evidence artifacts produced by the e2e tests.
# Lives under public/ so the deployed Worker serves these as static assets,
# accessible at /evidence/... on the live URL. Per-file binary churn is
# heavy, so the artifacts themselves are gitignored — regenerate locally
# with:
#   pnpm test:e2e:erp                            # ERP workflow walk-throughs
#   pnpm test:e2e --project=chromium             # standard e2e (admin-evidence + others)
#
# What lives here when the suite has run:
#   workflows/<workflow>/<step>.png              # per-step PNG snapshots
#   admin-pages/<route>.png                      # per-admin-page PNG snapshots
#   test-results/<spec>/<test>/video.webm        # per-test recording
#   test-results/<spec>/<test>/trace.zip         # per-test Playwright trace
#   _report/                                     # HTML reporter root

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
